item.title: We Interview Ed Jowett from Shades of Vengeance
item.description:
Eric sits down with Ed Jowett, managing director and lead games designer of Shades of Vengeance. Ed's newest game Era: Kaiju (a game where you get to play a giant monster) is currently on kickstarter.
